# CHANGELOG
#
# 0.2.0 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# New shield ship + shield factory.
# Added a focus beacon, which prioritises units to be placed near it.
# Added a Bertha weapon, which can fire powerful volleys to anywhere on the map.
# Most factories now have a final T5 upgrade.
# Factories display current and potential DPS.
# You can now sell all upgrades of a factory, or the factory itself.
# Fissures now slowly regenerate resources over time, to a maxmium value.
# Significantly improved performance of placement logic.
# Fissure Extractor boost now only increases resource consumption 1.5X.
# Refactor of factory upgrade logic. This allows for more interesting upgrades in the future.
# Added a keybind to toggle the Forge (Custom0).
#
# --- Bug fixes and minor changes ---
# Cannon damage radius upgrades now also increase shot_damage_count. This meant radius upgrades previously
# were useless.
# If a ship move has failed too many times, unitcontrol will now attempt to move a random ship. This should
# increase the overall density of ships on the frontline.
# The Fissure Extractor has a new animated sprite.
# Clicking reset now recalculates creeper frontlines as fast as possible (2 seconds).
# Fixed bug where dummy units were being killed by sand damage. This was causing ship placement to break.
# Fixed bug where a ship placement was considered ok if ship rect boxes perfectly overlapped. This was
# causing ships to move directly on top of each other.
# Fixed bug causing factory ship indicator references to not be properly removed
# Fixed bug where ships could be placed out of bounds
# Fixed bug preventing factories from being moved
# Improved frontline debug option to not reset every map iteration
#
